      Unlike  the Hindu festival of&nbsp;Diwali&nbsp;whose  significance is based on the texts and scriptures of&nbsp;Hinduism Bandi  Chhor Divas celebrates a Sikh historic event related to the sixth Guru,&nbsp;Guru Hargobind According to Sikh history, on this day, Guru Hargobind was  released from prison by the Mughal Emperor&nbsp;Jahangir&nbsp;who  freed 52 other Hindu kings with him.[5][6][7],<br />
